00:19:37.150 --> 00:19:42.060 align:middle line:84%
So I'm very interested
to hear what her side is.

00:19:42.060 --> 00:19:45.450 align:middle line:84%
And obviously, I will
tell her what happened

00:19:45.450 --> 00:19:47.520 align:middle line:90%
to me and my experience.

00:19:47.520 --> 00:19:51.180 align:middle line:84%
>> The universe has merged Vicki
and her father's paths together

00:19:51.180 --> 00:19:54.360 align:middle line:84%
in such a fantastical
and wondrous manner,

00:19:54.360 --> 00:19:57.150 align:middle line:84%
that it is almost
impossible to understand.

