life altering,

00:20:06.330 --> 00:20:09.280 align:middle line:90%
near-death experiences.

00:20:09.280 --> 00:20:16.290 align:middle line:84%
>> The first time that I heard
that you had died was a couple

00:20:16.290 --> 00:20:20.010 align:middle line:84%
