00:20:20.010 --> 00:20:22.140 align:middle line:90%
But I didn't want to ask.

00:20:22.140 --> 00:20:25.050 align:middle line:84%
I was kind of waiting
for that moment where

00:20:25.050 --> 00:20:26.700 align:middle line:84%
you felt comfortable
enough to tell me,

00:20:26.700 --> 00:20:29.490 align:middle line:84%
because it's such a
personal experience.

00:20:29.490 --> 00:20:31.710 align:middle line:90%
And it's life changing.

00:20:31.710 --> 00:20:37.320 align:middle line:84%
And it's so hard to tell someone
that this is what happened,

