00:21:01.560 --> 00:21:05.310 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, personally, I can
tell you now that I think

00:21:05.310 --> 00:21:07.125 align:middle line:90%
I've fulfilled my purpose.

00:21:07.125 --> 00:21:09.950 align:middle line:90%


